sections.heading: to 69-34-12 - Repealed.
sections.text: Repeals.— Laws 1987, ch. 234, § 84 repealed 69-34-1 to 69-34-12 NMSA 1978, as enacted by Laws 1933, ch. 153, §§ 275, 278 to 280, 282, 284, and 285, relating to electrical equipment in mines other than coal, effective July 1, 1987. For present comparable provisions,see69-8-1 to 69-8-15 NMSA 1978.
